## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of the sources reviewed. The findings are based on a selection of articles and may not encompass all possible strategies for improving mental health care access. Additionally, the effectiveness of the proposed strategies may vary based on regional and cultural contexts. Further research and localized studies are recommended to tailor these strategies to specific populations and settings.

